Event Payload Description <code>donation.created</code> <code>DonationEventPayload</code> New donation received <pre><code>interface DonationEventPayload {
    id: string
    eventId: string
    amount: number // in cents
    donorName: string // "Anonymous" if hidden
    message?: string
    createdAt: string
}
</code></pre> <pre><code>socket.on('donation.created', (donation) =&gt; {
    console.log(`${donation.donorName} donated ${donation.amount / 100}€`)
})
</code></pre>
